divs: Sighting DetailsI was coming home from work and saw this over I-470 in Ohio as I came across the I-470 bridge from WV. I saw this and I carry a camera around with me most of the time. I pulled over and took these photos. There were a few others that pulled over also and was using cell phones to film it. It was there for about 20 sec's and then took off to the north and out of site. Funny part is that it was silent.
Summary: Coming across bridge into Ohio I saw this over the I-470, I stopped and took a photo
trends: There have been no other sightings in Bellaire
This sighting has never been favorited.
